To use cntlm for proxy config:

* For Windows:
   - Download cntlm from http://cntlm.sourceforge.net/
   - After download run setup.exe installer
   - Afer installation, you have to locate the configuration file, in Windows it should be %PROGRAMFILES%\Cntlm\cntlm.ini (usually C:\Program Files\Cntlm\cntlm.ini).
   - 